{"id":144303,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/媒体频繁出现背景谬误/","date":"2011-04-12T17:30:08Z","modified":"2011-04-12T18:15:02Z","title":"媒体频繁出现背景谬误","content":"<p>中国因为美国发表了中国人权报告而发表了美国人权纪录。今天国内媒体继续在人权问题上抨击美国，例如“美国说人权，地球人都笑了”，乌有之乡著名作家孔庆东称“美国人权记录很糟糕”，“中方促美勿用人权干涉内政”，“美国人权报告无视自身问题点名批评近百国家遭中俄反驳”。被限制上网的wmr称，这些媒体的报道都犯了一个逻辑错误：用攻击的方法回应批评，在本不相干的信念与该信念持有者的背景之间加以牵连，拉丁术语&#8221;tu quoque&#8221;（意思是&#8221;你是另一个&#8221;），常被用来命名这种人身攻击论证的背景谬误。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/14251e1e/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E9%A2%91%E7%B9%81%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E8%B0%AC%E8%AF%AF&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F04%2F12%2F1430242%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E9%A2%91%E7%B9%81%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E8%B0%AC%E8%AF%AF&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F04%2F12%2F1430242%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/100170248618/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14251e1e/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/100170248618/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14251e1e/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=3ZEJf_v698M:P9NgijTslew:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=3ZEJf_v698M:P9NgijTslew:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=